<h2>What is Desco Lead CRM?</h2>
<p>Desco Lead CRM is a professional SaaS platform built for automated Facebook and Instagram Lead Ads management. It receives leads in real-time through Meta Webhooks, stores them securely, and provides a comprehensive dashboard for managing the entire sales pipeline.</p>

<div class="info-card highlight">
  <h4><i class="fas fa-rocket"></i> Our Mission</h4>
  <p>To provide small and medium businesses with a powerful, secure, and easy-to-use CRM that automates lead collection from social media advertising and streamlines customer management.</p>
</div>

