<h2>Technology Stack</h2>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Backend:</strong> Node.js, Express.js</li>
  <li><strong>Database:</strong> PostgreSQL (Supabase)</li>
  <li><strong>ORM:</strong> Prisma</li>
  <li><strong>Hosting:</strong> Railway</li>
  <li><strong>API:</strong> Meta Graph API v25.0</li>
  <li><strong>Real-time:</strong> WebSockets</li>
  <li><strong>Notifications:</strong> Telegram Bot API</li>
  <li><strong>Security:</strong> HMAC-SHA256, HTTPS, Session Authentication</li>
</ul>

